data.description: Beautifully updated Split-Level Home you will want to see! Main level includes Updated Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and custom cabinetry with built in wine rack, large Livingroom and Separate Dining room.  On the upper level you will find 3 Large Bedrooms and an Updated bath. On the lower level you have a big family room with built in shelving for extra comfort, a recently updated bath with Shower and bluetooth speaker system, storage, and laundry room with access to attached 2 car garage. W&D Stays.
